@*Movie - Exit 8 | Genre - Horror | Thoughts - Having been based on an indie game with no dialogue or story, Exit 8 needed to add a lot of extra details to justify its runtime. 
These extra details could have ended up feeling disjointed or unnecessary, but instead they were woven together in a way thatdoes not interfere with the spirit of the original game or the tone of the movie.
The movie is not scaryso much as it is unsettling, but it still makes for an interesting watch. | 
Real Facts - None of the characters in Exit 8 have names, and the movie's credits simply list them with titles like Lost Man for the main character
